"للمؤشر 15-3-1 من مؤشرات أهداف التنمية المستدامة] "
"(https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-sdg-"
"indicator-1531-proportion-land-degraded-over-total-land) معلومات شاملة عن"
" مستويات المستويات."

#: ../../SO1.md:1013
msgid "1.3.3. Reporting process and step-by-step procedure"
msgstr "1-3-3 عملية الإبلاغ والإجراءات التدريجية"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:1015
msgid ""
"For the 2026 national reporting process, the following information for "
