# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:1063
msgid "Options to improve estimation of changes in SOC stocks include:"
msgstr ""
"تشمل خيارات تحسين تقدير التغيرات في مخزونات المركبات العضوية الثابتة ما "
"يلي:"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:1065
msgid ""
"Assess spatial and temporal validity of default land cover change and "
