# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:1070
msgid ""
"A detailed description of the Tier 2 method is provided in section "
"5.2.6.2 of the [Good Practice Guidance for SDG Indicator "
"15.3.1](https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-sdg-"
"indicator-1531-proportion-land-degraded-over-total-land). In addition, "
"section 3.3.1 of the [Addendum](https://www.unccd.int/resources/manuals-"
