# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:1126
msgid ""
"This step is required if the UNCCD default data are not used (i.e.,if a "
"user specific modified tier 1 or a tier 2 approach is adopted). Changes "
"in SOC stocks over time are modeled using land cover conversion "
"coefficients as proxies for land use, meaning that accurate "
"identification of land cover transitions is essential for reliable "
