# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:1174
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If the default UNCCD data are used, then table SO1-3.T1 is automatically "
"pre-filled with estimates of SOC (in tonnes per hectare) in the topsoil "
"for each of the seven default land cover classes for the reference, "
"baseline and reporting periods. If Parties use alternative national data "
"they should provide these values and also provide basic metadata (see "
"{doc}`Annex II <annex_II>`) for the datasets to be used in the Data "
