"sub-indicators, calculate the extent of degradation in the baseline "
"period and in the two reporting periods (2019 and 2023 respectively). The"
" extent of degradation in the reporting periods is calculated by summing "
"(i) areas of land where changes in the sub-indicators are considered to "
"indicate new degradation; and (ii) areas of land that have persisted in a"
" degraded state since the baseline period (i.e. have not improved to a "
"non-degraded state)."
